		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			I love this spell.  The constant damage sucks an enormous amont of damage from the affected target.  Every three to five seconds, the life meter lowers on the target.  It seems to do this three times.  Then I normally recast the spell.  For some low level creatures, such as Orc raiders, this is all that is needed to kill them.  You don't even need to swing.  On higher level creatures, this can help you and your pet take on yellow creatures.  But, don't try this too often.... the spell can fail and then you have a ticked off yellow creature after you.  Thank heavens for Gate...
			</font>
	
